<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/136037-slow-read-for-me-tried-to-get-through-it">Slow read for me tried to get through it couldn&#39;t ...anybody else? Maybe I will try again...I really love Francine Roberts but this did not work for me...</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_136037'><a id="like_count_community_question_136037" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/136037?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">5 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F95617.A_Voice_in_the_Wind">like</a></span>

